{
  "stem": "9963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in a barrack you could sleep up to 250 to 300 people in one barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] They gave us in the morning black coffee with one piece of bread-- what was a few ounces-- maybe it were about three ounces of bread-- with a piece of margarine-- not all the time the margarine.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The bread with the coffee was the every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The margarine, sometimes we got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the evening, just a little bit soup-- very, very thin soup, what-- that hot water, like they say-- was better than nothing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's all food what we got.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with that food, we had to work very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in that particular camp, again, we were making roads, pushing mountain away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were digging stones from the mountains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had this-- on-- in that particular camp, we laid down in the mountains-- it was a mountain about 10 stories high.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a ledge like this to stand up and to digging out the stones from the mountains, throw them down, down the-- down such a way-- people with the-- breaking them up, put them in a machine where the machine ground it.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was to make the roads-- the stones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On that mountain, many people died, because when somebody fall down from that ledge, was nothing more to pick up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they didn't even bother to go to pick him up, because he was gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was so high and so treacherous that it was not worth to pick up.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
